Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Robyn] This is your fault. You\Nrealize that. Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All I wanted was to bring people together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To give them a chance at a better life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But you-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Me? I am a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll admit I was duped. Used!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And although my hands may not be clean,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,at least I am not a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- He didn't kill anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am not gonna stand\Nhere and be lectured
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,by some snake with a mustache who helped
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that man tear us all apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Watts] Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- I suppose we're\Nall stuck in it together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Just speak for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the right people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Whitley has\Nreached out to my legal team
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and will have me out of\Nhere before you can say-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Robyn] Shut up.\N(barrier thuds)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- You do realize you've already caught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- I hate not being able to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- We can do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can kill the man who put us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Reporter] With still no word
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,from General Ironwood, Mantle\Ncitizens are frightened
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and perplexed by the sudden withdrawal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of military personnel,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,especially given the massive Grimm horde
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,outside the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anything quite like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It truly feels like the end of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Atlas Eye is committed\Nto updating the public,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,until our dying-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Citizens of Mantle! General\NIronwood has abandoned you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but we have not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can hear this, gather\Nany food and supplies you need
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to stay warm then head\Nto the Mantle Crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grimm are starting to make\Ntheir way back into the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can hold the line\N(guns firing)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,if we all come together.\N(body thuds)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't, well, you've all\Nseen what's waiting for us out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to show your teeth Mantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- All right. The others\Nare definitely missing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Oscar] Yang! Yang no! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Only take what you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- The crater? Are you\Nsure it's safe out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Absolutely ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Heads up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Way better than a hover bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Have the Grimm already\Npushed this far in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, I think those were\Nmore from last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ren! If Jaune hits you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:06:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,with his Aura Amp, think\Nyou can mask everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ren] We can give it a shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is a lengthy trip through Mantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, no, that's a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have a Grimm free journey\Nall the way to the crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do we really got a shack\Nup with those animals down
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in the slums? I'd feel a\Nlot safer being up in Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, I'm sure you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But the people up top\Nhave decided
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not worth the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Faunus, on the\Nother hand, have been willing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to lend all the help they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of whether or not you deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- So, I'll just... I'll\Ngo get our things then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Civilian] I don't want to go to the slums.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Civilian's Daughter] Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Civilian] General Ironwood said we\Nwere going to Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Civilian's Daughter] You're setting a bad example!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Oscar] It should not be this\Nhard getting people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:06:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to just cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Civilian] She didn't need to yell at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Civilian's Daughter] Mother, it's fine. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ozpin] And yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it's something I'm becoming\Nincreasingly concerned about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know I really don't need\Nyour additional commentary
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ozpin] You all have\Nevery right to be upset,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,especially you Oscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I left you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm not upset that you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm upset you came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I started to feel like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the same me I was before all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but, the me I always wanted to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt, like I was actually part the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ozpin] I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But even though it may not have felt
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,like I was with you, I\Nwas never truly gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gaining control
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of my remaining magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,recollecting my longest held memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means our two souls are still
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,on the inevitable path to becoming one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- But, I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ozpin] Neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, you good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's just a lot to focus on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- You can do it Ren.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost to the Crater-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't need a pep talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ozpin] We need to find\Na way to work together,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,not just the two of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[May] - All right, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thanks again for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- [May] Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Once Robyn learned
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,about Amity Tower, she\Nwouldn't shut up about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever she is, I'm sure\Nshe would want us doing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,what we can to get it up in the air
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and get the world talking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Fiona's got your\Nfriends helping out in my stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ruby] Are you sure this is safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Weiss] Snowshoe Shipping is an SDC subsidiary,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning all the drones here report
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to the company, not the general.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The pneumatic tubes allow for\NDust refined in the crater
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to be sent straight up to Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need to find the\None for the military base.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are there any buildings in Atlas
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that your family doesn't own?\N(Nora chuckling)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- That isn't relevant at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ruby] Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- I do not like it when friends fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:09:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yang and I might not agree on\Nhow best to save Mantle but-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Penny] No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean Winter. The general.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They were our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But then the Ace Ops attacked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And the general, he said\Npeople were going to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- That was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was only saying it to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- I was the protector of Mantle,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but now, I am much more than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wish I was not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- But, you're still you Penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,By becoming the Winter Maiden\Nyou did protect Mantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Nora] I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- I suppose there's no turning back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Between our secret weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and my semblance, you all\Ncouldn't be in better hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- So how do we use this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- It should be simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lie back in the tube
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and press launch-\N(Weiss screaming)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- No Crimson, I need you and\Nyour team over in Sector 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mantle police are helping\Nus clear the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're going to need backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're doing great Fi.\NRobyn would be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- I feel like you should\Nbe doing this after flexing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,on the news like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- (chuckling) How else was I\Nsupposed to get the word out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides it seems to be working.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's this group coming in from?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Yang] That would be Sector 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- You cleared 7 already? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:12:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I wasn't\Nsure how you'd be doing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,without all of your teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, as you can see\Nwe're doing just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- But where are you putting everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're working to get\Nmost of them settled
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in houses or other shelters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A large portion of the\Ncommunity is also trying
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to get old mine shafts\Ninto a livable condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Joanna] We've got a lot of people to keep warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Looting the SDC refineries\Nis our best source of dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately no one's getting\Narrested during the apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just knowing those Grimm are circling
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,out there doesn't feel great.\NWhat are they waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Fi's Uncle] Fi!\N(man panting)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- We got another fight breaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Crap. Thanks uncle. We'll\Nhandle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll handle it. You've\Ngot enough to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Crimson] Fiona? Crimson again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We spotted a decent sized\Ngroup of Grimm moving in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,from the east. Can't take\Nthem with all these civies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, for crying out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Yang] Did he say east?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Yang] Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Jaune] Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay Fiona. That's one\Nmore problem taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Fiona] Good, cause\Nwe're getting reports
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of more Grimm coming in from the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Huntsmen there could\Nreally use some backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay. We're on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's all the negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:13:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Salem's forces aren't moving in,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's enough to start\Nattracting the stragglers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Guys, we're not finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- All right. We need to\Nhurry this up and take-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- They ran. I've never seen\NGrimm act that way before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- But what were they running from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oscar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:15:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oscar!\N(engine revving)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait! It's using Oscar as a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- But grim aren't that smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Grimm] - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Did it just?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Fiona] Kids, what's your status?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,West side's taking damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Fiona] Kids. what's your status?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Yang] We've got an emergency,\Nwe're not going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Fiona] What? What kind of emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- You wouldn't believe me if I told you.
